## 05 — Database Schema: Supabase Tables

### 🏢 `businesses`

| Column | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `id` | `uuid` **PK** | Unique business identifier |
| `name` | `text` | Registered business name |
| `ops_number` | `text` | WhatsApp ops number (agent handles) |
| `primary_number` | `text` | Owner's WhatsApp (agent reports here) |
| `gemini_context` | `jsonb` | Business-specific AI persona config |
| `subscription_tier` | `text` | `starter` \| `growth` \| `enterprise` |
| `created_at` | `timestamptz` | Account creation timestamp |

### 💬 `conversations`

| Column | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `id` | `uuid` **PK** | Conversation thread ID |
| `business_id` | `uuid` **FK** | Owning business |
| `contact_wa_id` | `text` | Customer WhatsApp ID |
| `status` | `text` | `active` \| `escalated` \| `closed` \| `paused` |
| `last_message_at` | `timestamptz` | Last activity timestamp |
| `escalation_reason` | `text` | Why it was escalated (nullable) |
| `agent_context` | `jsonb` | Rolling conversation summary for AI |

### 📨 `messages`

| Column | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `id` | `uuid` **PK** | Message record ID |
| `conversation_id` | `uuid` **FK** | Parent conversation |
| `direction` | `text` | `inbound` \| `outbound` |
| `role` | `text` | `user` \| `agent` \| `human_agent` |
| `body` | `text` | Message text content |
| `media_url` | `text` | Attached media (nullable) |
| `wa_message_id` | `text` | WhatsApp message ID for receipt tracking |

### ⚡ `agent_actions`

| Column | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `id` | `uuid` **PK** | Action log ID |
| `conversation_id` | `uuid` **FK** | Related conversation |
| `action_type` | `text` | `query` \| `insert` \| `update` \| `delete` \| `escalate` \| `notify` |
| `payload` | `jsonb` | Full action payload sent/received |
| `status` | `text` | `pending` \| `success` \| `failed` |
| `executed_at` | `timestamptz` | Execution timestamp |

